{"id": 1444, "genre": 1001, "title": "在出门旅行这件事上，你有什么前车之鉴？", "description": "带错东西，信错推荐，出门在外谁还没有过几把辛酸泪呢？（题图来自：Chelsea Beck）", "record_count": 4661, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170112154532HqJ4j6lzgCYFNWuy.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-26T03:00:43Z", "options": [{"id": 170240, "content": "别去丽江的酒吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911176}, {"id": 158721, "content": "得有钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916784}, {"id": 158722, "content": "严重衣服带不够患者（出门前减减减，冷了买买买）", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808790}, {"id": 161538, "content": "有硬卧就别买硬座", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924717}, {"id": 158723, "content": "赶火车一定要 早点出发！看准时间！最后一分钟赶到整个人要疯了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803592}, {"id": 158725, "content": "别坐午夜航班，虽然省钱但太累不值得～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898247}, {"id": 158726, "content": "带孩子的话一定要住的好，选择的城市那里一定要有适合孩子吃的饭菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916778}, {"id": 160778, "content": "没什么经验啊。  打算今年独自去香港或者东南亚那里旅行一下。其实内心更想和前女友去的但已经分手了....只好自己去咯……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922176}, {"id": 158731, "content": "懒人不要穷游，别想什么风景都一次看够，旅行结束的时候把你在景点的文明素质也带回去。", "image": "img/option/option/20170126230725LIs8SWpR3Nqw7K2h.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916827}, {"id": 158732, "content": "带个超大容量没电的充电宝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916832}, {"id": 159244, "content": "一定要双数，不要单数！同路人要互补合拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909879}, {"id": 164108, "content": "想象的是自己在幽静的小路上散步，结果是和一堆人挤着散步，寸步难行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930274}, {"id": 158734, "content": "我去爬山为什么要带卷发棒……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831557}, {"id": 160014, "content": "不要把东西忘在车上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781562}, {"id": 160526, "content": "要有A计划和B计划以应付不同的困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921488}, {"id": 158735, "content": "按平时的节奏吃饭，不要图省钱自己带食品。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916839}, {"id": 159248, "content": "一定要做好规划，随身带点现金", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268635}, {"id": 158737, "content": "别相信攻略～因为每个人的旅行都是自己的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914587}, {"id": 159761, "content": "心态决定景色，不要和旅伴闹脾气，即使很累", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919564}, {"id": 159506, "content": "自己一个人最享受", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910656}, {"id": 168978, "content": "要想考虑两个人是否能在一起过日子，带他（她）去旅行！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917645}, {"id": 159251, "content": "尽量选择自由行，哪怕一次只去一个城市，最少住5天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904437}, {"id": 170259, "content": "找一个身体健康和有良好生活习惯的旅伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898700}, {"id": 158740, "content": "别去丽江，", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889364}, {"id": 158741, "content": "学生证和身份证要保住", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879053}, {"id": 159253, "content": "必要的东西带好，能少带就少带。出差多了，常规清单是个很必要的，会减少很多的麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724853}, {"id": 158745, "content": "北方景点到处椰壳饰品，南方纪念品满眼俄罗斯套娃，米粒刻字遍布全国。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892722}, {"id": 159257, "content": "最好还是结伴而行 两人都懂当地语言最好 也不要跟团  毕竟自己探索最有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917795}, {"id": 161049, "content": "提前规划，千万别跟人AA，否则连早点钱都要平摊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207675}, {"id": 158746, "content": "要带数据线～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915487}, {"id": 160794, "content": "行李吧，能少就少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922218}, {"id": 158747, "content": "有钱有时间就好，其他你都可以不用太过在意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270503}, {"id": 160027, "content": "防晒别只照顾脸 紫外线高的地方要你命", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920308}, {"id": 166684, "content": "带够钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936908}, {"id": 158749, "content": "千万别去用旅行检验准男友/女友，\n分分钟虐死自己…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812464}, {"id": 158750, "content": "要有好同伴", "image": "img/option/option/20170127001049PDeBpS6E8KqG2xt0", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916623}, {"id": 160542, "content": "别和当地人吵架。住宿一定要干净舒服。随身行李能少则少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921517}, {"id": 158751, "content": "要有好同伴", "image": "img/option/option/20170127001101hGvQX9Uy1a8DsrJn", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916623}, {"id": 159263, "content": "如果是一个人出去旅游，一定要控制好时间周期，太长了你会烦的，相信我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894397}, {"id": 159008, "content": "找个同行的异性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878639}, {"id": 160288, "content": "合适的伙伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920944}, {"id": 158753, "content": "准备好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216219}, {"id": 160289, "content": "以后月抛首选不再是丽江了，怕毁容", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920933}, {"id": 188705, "content": "别在节假日去旅游景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995155}, {"id": 158754, "content": "一个人出行可以选择住青旅。因为可以遇到志同道合的玩伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912524}, {"id": 178466, "content": "多带点好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919839}, {"id": 182050, "content": "别跟路边导游\n提前订酒店\n下雨天尽量别去人流量大的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977808}, {"id": 160035, "content": "不要觉得是孝敬老人就和他们一起出去，亲身体验没有共同语言，沟通很累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920307}, {"id": 160036, "content": "一定要做好计划，要有耐心，不然就颓了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897285}, {"id": 163364, "content": "一定得把各种APP用起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926813}]}